cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.SE, cs.LG, cs.CY 

This paper deals with natural language processing (NLP) techniques for automating the user request management process. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language), which deals with NLP and related topics. The paper also involves machine learning techniques for predicting ticket escalation and assigning tickets to developers, which falls under the categories of cs.IR (Information Retrieval) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also deals with software engineering practices, which falls under the category of cs.SE (Software Engineering). Finally, the paper involves cybersecurity, which falls under the category of cs.CY (Computers and Society).
